quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  38,43,"And We bestowed on him his family, and the like of them with them, a mercy from Us, and a Reminding to ones endowed with intellects"
  38,44,"And (we said) \"Take in your hand a jumble of rushes, then strike therewith, and do not break (your oath).\" Surely We found him a patient (man). How excellent a bondman he was! Surely he was a constant resorter (to Us)"
  38,45,"And remember Our bondmen Ibrahim and Ishaq and Yaaqub, (Abraham, Isaac and Jacob, respectively) (men) endowed with achievements and be holdings (Literally: with hands and eyesight\"s)"
  38,46,"Surely We made them faithful with the (exclusively sincere) faith, the Reminding of the Residence (i.e., the Hereafter)"
  38,47,"And surely in Our Providence they are indeed of the elected, the most charitable (i.e., the best)"
  38,48,"And remember Shuaayb, (Ishmael) and Alyasaca and Thalkifli; and each is among the most charitable"
  38,49,This is a Remembrance; and surely for the pious is indeed a fair resorting
  38,50,Gardens of Adn (Eden) whereof the gates are open for them
  38,51,"Reclining therein, they call for many fruits and (cool) drink therein"
  38,52,And in their presence are (maidens) restraining their glances (and) like of age
  38,53,This is what you are promised for the Day of Reckoning
  38,54,Surely this is indeed Our provision; in no way will it suffer depletion
  38,55,"This is (for the righteous); and surely for the inordinate (i.e., tyrants) there will indeed be an evil resorting"
  38,56,"Hell, wherein they roast, miserable then is the cradling"
  38,57,"This is (their reward); so let them taste it: scalding (water) and constantly (overflowing) pus"
  38,58,And other (torments) of like kind paired together
  38,59,This is a troop rushing along with you; there is no welcome for them; surely they will be roasting in the Fire
  38,60,"They will say, \"No indeed, it is you (who) have no welcome; you forwarded it for us; so, miserable is the reposing"
  38,61,"They will say, \"Our Lord, whoever forwarded this for us, then doubly increase torment for him in the Fire"